<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221180>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Adults and nymphs of Aphthargelia rumbleboredomia on Aconogonon phytolaccifolium. Note to the right is a paler somewhat elongate aphid, which is a nymph of Capitophorus essigi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221181>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2 – 7. Aphthargelia rumbleboredomia: 2, aptera; 3, alate vivipara; 4, ovipara; Aphthargelia symphoricarpi: 5, aptera; 6, alate vivipara; 7, ovipara." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

